resources.string: All calculations are approximate. When buying wheels, do not rely entirely on the results of calculations especially if the purchase takes place without fitting. Install wheels in accordance with the vehicle manufacturer\'s recommendations.
Depending on the design of the rims, the calculated outer and inner boundaries of the wheels may be inaccurate, and the structural elements of the rim can protrude beyond these boundaries.
